OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBarry Sheerman:            
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FLongest-serving Labour MP  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fto step down               
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, One of the country's longest-serving   
OL,6, MPs has announced he will step down at 
OL,7, the next election.                     
OL,9,FBarry Sheerman, 81, who has been Labour
OL,10,FMP for Huddersfield since 1979, said it
OL,11,Fhad been "the honour of my life".      
OL,13,FThe former select committee chair said 
OL,14,Fstanding down at the next election was 
OL,15,Fthe right time for him and the party.  
OL,17,FMr Sheerman added he was proud of the  
OL,18,Fwork he had done over the past 42 years
OL,19,Fbut was looking forward to spending    
OL,20,Fmore time with his family.             
